  "texts": [
    "The features extracted by CNN are filtered into DWT for refinement and afterwards being fed into the Support Vector Machine classifier, while the output of the same CNNs is fed to U-Net for segmentation.",
    "In this way, dual tasks will guarantee comprehensive analysis in terms of identification and localization of cancerous tissues.",
    "These methods are deliberately chosen to balance computational efficiency, accuracy, and interpretability.",
    "The framework is, therefore, highly effective for the CKHK-22 dataset of medium size.",
    "A combination of these strengths makes the PolynetDWTCADx a reliable and clinically relevant solution in detecting and segmenting colorectal cancer diagnosis."
  ],
